181
00:08:27,110 --> 00:08:29,730
Tak co, Shido?

182
00:08:29,730 --> 00:08:31,610
Jsi vzrušený?

183
00:08:31,610 --> 00:08:33,400
No...

184
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:34,030
Jo.

185
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:34,780
